{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idd22fb549-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4554"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4554"},"text":"§ 4554.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Regulations and orders","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd22fb54a-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4554/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subject to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s4559"},"text":"section 4559 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and subsection (b), the President may prescribe such regulations and issue such orders as the President may determine to be appropriate to carry out this chapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd22fb54b-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s4554/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Procurement regulations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Any procurement regulation, procedure, or form issued pursuant to subsection (a) shall be issued pursuant to section 25 of the Office of Federal Procurement Policy Act [now ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t41/s1302"},"text":"41 U.S.C. 1302","children":[],"tail":", 1303], and shall conform to any governmentwide procurement policy or regulation issued pursuant to section 6 or 25 of that Act [see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t41/s1121"},"text":"41 U.S.C. 1121","children":[],"tail":" et seq., 1302, 1303]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idd22fb54c-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1950-09-08/ch932"},"text":"Sept. 8, 1950, ch. 932","children":[],"tail":", title VII, § 704, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/816"},"text":"64 Stat. 816","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1951-07-31/ch275"},"text":"July 31, 1951, ch. 275","children":[],"tail":", title I, § 109(c), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/65/139"},"text":"65 Stat. 139","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/558/tI/s134"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–558, title I, § 134","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/4212"},"text":"106 Stat. 4212","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idd22fb54d-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"prospectiveAmendment","id":"idd22fb54e-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Termination of Section","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For termination of section, see ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s4564/a"},"text":"section 4564(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idd22fb54f-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idd22fb550-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in subsec. (a), was in the original “this Act”, meaning ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1950-09-08/ch932"},"text":"act Sept. 8, 1950, ch. 932","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/798"},"text":"64 Stat. 798","children":[],"tail":", known as the Defense Production Act of 1950, which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s4501"},"text":"section 4501 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Sections 6 and 25 of the Office of Federal Procurement Policy Act, referred to in subsec. (b), were sections 6 and 25 of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/400"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–400","children":[],"tail":", which were classified to sections 405 and 421, respectively, of former Title 41, Public Contracts, and were repealed and largely restated in subchapter II (§ 1121 et seq.) of chapter 11 and as sections 1302 and 1303 of Title 41, Public Contracts, by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/350"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–350","children":[],"tail":", §§ 3, 7(b), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2011-01-04"},"text":"Jan. 4, 2011","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/3677"},"text":"124 Stat. 3677","children":[],"tail":", 3855."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idd22fb551-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to section 2154 of the former Appendix to this title prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idd22fb552-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1992—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/558"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–558","children":[],"tail":" amended section generally, substituting present provisions for provisions authorizing promulgation of rules, regulations, and orders by the President in order to carry out this chapter."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1951—Act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1951-07-31"},"text":"July 31, 1951","children":[],"tail":", limited authority to regulate natural gas where a State agency is handling the matter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idd22fb553-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idd22fb554-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1992 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/558"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–558","children":[],"tail":" deemed to have become effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-03-01"},"text":"Mar. 1, 1992","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/558/s304"},"text":"section 304 of Pub. L. 102–558","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s4502"},"text":"section 4502 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"idd22fb555-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"te